. days is longer than daze), as well as gradient paradigm uniformity, in which the frequency of related words is expected to have an influence on paradigm members (e.g. day influences days). Findings from these studies contribute to a growing body of research in the field of morphophonetics.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 4aMorphologie ‹Lingustik›. 4aPhonologie. 4aReduktion ‹Lingustik›. 4aSprache. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / Morphology.2bisacsh  aLanguage.  amorphology.  aphonology.  areduction.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022 Englishz978311099370708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022z9783110993684oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831110180960 cprintz978311101293340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783111017754zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783111017754zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783111017754/original  a978-3-11-099370-7 EBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-117578-2 DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DSPb2022  aZDB-23-GOA